      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ONTARIO (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and six minors from 20 tries. In the money last time at this track (22.27) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 4.5 lengths second. Rates on top and should go close. LITTLE LOCKETT (4) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 6 length win at this track in a handy 17.89. Awkwardly drawn but goes well at this distance. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. MERMAID SHIMMER (6) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Grade 4/5/MDN winner two back at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. SO NAIVE (2) can fill a top-three spot.",
